commit.message:
Added splash screen, faction choosing

Faction choosing still buggy

Data structures

There is now a node struct, and an array called nodes. It contains:
data (arbitrary, will need to be parsed depending on which mode, application specific),
node number (unique address),
mode,
last seen time
you can just say 'fixed' or something

Application can send and receive

Sends packets at 2Hz interval

Added another test program (changes lights with each receive)

Uses: display, 3 x neopixels, LED, wireless module (receiving)

Added neopixel test code

Works with one WS2812, green color (at least). Plan to test with two soon
Added counter to transmit code - definitely sending data correctly
